https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c2756%2c20220906%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,111,聲,2756,20220906,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"2756","JDATE":"20220906","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}